Description: srtmerge is a Python library used to merge two Srt files.
        
        Usage
        =====
        
        ::
        
            from srtmerge import srtmerge
            srtmerge([filepath1, filepath2, ...], out_filepath, offset=1000)
        
        srtmerge filepath1 filepath2 out_filepath offset=1000
        
